---
import { Text } from "../components/atoms/text/text";
import Layout from "../components/layout.astro";
import { Aside } from "../components/layout/aside/aside";
import nodoka from "../assets/nodoka.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<style>
  main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-24);

    padding: var(--spacing-48) var(--spacing-256); 
    color: var(--color-grayscale-50);
    background: var(--color-grayscale-900);
  }

  .profile {
    width: 128px;
    height: 128px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (width <= 1024px) {
     main {
      padding: var(--spacing-48) var(--spacing-128); 
    }
  }

  @media (width <= 768px) {
    main {
      padding: var(--spacing-48) var(--spacing-24);
    }
  }
</style>

<Layout>
  <main>
    <Text mode="h2">About me</Text>
    <Image src={nodoka} alt="A portrait of Nodoka" width={352} height={352} class="profile" />
    <Text mode="h2">Profile</Text>
    <div>
    <Text mode="body">1996年生まれ、岩手県出身。</Text>
    <Text mode="body">大学卒業後に旅行会社の商品企画部での業務を経て、ウェブマーケティング企業にて5年ほどSEOを担当。通信・デジタルサービス領域の比較メディアを中心に、コンテンツ企画・編集やユーザー行動データの分析、UI/UX改善に携わる。HTML・CSSの知識を活かした情報設計と、データに基づくユーザー体験の改善を強みとする。基本情報技術者試験合格、Google UXデザイン認定資格取得。</Text>
    </div>
    <Text mode="body">Born in 1996 in Iwate, Japan. After working in the product planning department of a travel company, spent five years handling SEO at a web marketing company. Works on content planning and editing, user behavior analysis, and UI/UX improvements for comparison media focused on telecommunications and digital services. Skilled in information design using HTML and CSS and in improving user experience through data-driven insights. Holds the Fundamental Information Technology Engineer certification and completed the Google UX Design program.</Text>

    <div>
      <Text mode="h2">Like</Text>
      <Text mode="body">美術館、クライミング、動物</Text>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
